參考書目 References


備註 Remarks
     ~觸媒之發展與應用  ( Spring 2014 )

授課老師：翁鴻山、陳炳宏
 

Part I   ------------------------------------------ 翁鴻山
1. Catalysts and Catalysis (觸媒與催化作用)
2. Catalyst Preparation and Manufacture (觸媒之製備與生產)
3. Temperature-programming Methods (程溫方法)
4.  Supported Metal Catalysts (金屬擔體觸媒)
5.  Acid and Zeolite Catalysts (酸性與沸石觸媒)
6.  Nano, Mesoporous and Monolithic Catalysts (奈米、中孔洞與塊狀觸媒)
7.  Laboratory Reactors and Experimental Methods (實驗室反應器及實驗方法)
8.  The Selected Applied Catalysts (觸媒應用例)
 a. Fertilizers-ammonia (氨與氨肥)
b. Steam reforming of methane (甲烷之蒸氣重組)  
9.  Catalysts for Cleaner Production Processes and Environmental Protection
     (應用於清潔製程及環保的觸媒)
10.  Catalysts for Energy-related Technologies (Including photo-catalysts and catalysts for fuel cells) (應用於能源科技的觸媒，包括光觸媒及用於燃料電池的觸媒)

Part II   ----------------------------------------- 陳炳宏
1. Characterization of Catalytic Materials:  
 Gas Adsorption, Vibration Spectroscopy, X-ray Spectroscopy, Electron Spectroscopy, Ion Spectroscopy
(觸媒材料的特性鑑定: 氣體吸附，振動光譜，X射線光譜，電子能譜，離子能譜)
4. Applications:
CO oxidation, Nano Carbon Materials, Hydrogen Production, etc.
(應用: CO氧化，納米碳材料，產氫等)
3. Operando spectroscopy (耦合量測催化特性光譜法)

References
 Satterfield :  Heterogeneous Catalysis in Industrial Practice
 Bond :  Heterogeneous Catalysis, Principles and Application
 Thomas : Principles and Practice of Heterogeneous Catalysis
 Niemantsverdriet : Concepts of Modern Catalysis and Kinetics (Wiley20007)
 Rothenburg :  Catalysis-Concepts and Green Applications (Wiley2008)

